* Fix spelling mistake
* Stock zones follows a fill-first methodologythe current zone is filled with instances before other zones are considered. This adds a flag to nova to select a spread-first methodology. The implementation is simply adding a random.shuffle() prior to sorting the list of potential compute hosts by weights
